blogPost.excerpt:
This is part of our If Everything Was Like Among Us videos! We're so excited for the new Airships map. Who else thinks Among Us in real life would be so cool! 🙋‍♀️

Thank you to the Portland Spirit for letting us film on their boat! https://www.portlandspirit.com

Thanks to Cooper Grey from She's Alaska for helping us with this song! His channel https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCcveoEbcHSG8M_uhWmJAhkg

If you like  The Norris Nuts, Dixie D'Amelio, or the Txunamy, you'll love our channel. We do funny pranks, songs, and skits!

Shiloh's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/shilohanelson/   
Elijah's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/iamelijahnelson/
Micah's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/heythisismicah/?hl=en
Judah's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/judahnelson/?hl=en
Britney's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/britneyleighnelson/
Aislinn's Instagram https://www.instagram.com/aislinnelimcc/?hl=en

Song credits: 
Songwriters: Cooper Grey (from She’s Alaska), Shiloh & Bros, Elijah Nelson, Shiloh Nelson, Britney Nelson
Track Production, Mixing and Mastering: Diego Fernandes
Producer: David Nelson 


Subscribe here! http://bit.ly/ShilohToJudahChannel

Hit the bell to be notified when we post new videos! 

#amongus #imposteramongus #inreallife

localize.title: IMPOSTORS - 在我们中间的歌曲
localize.description:
这是我们《如果一切都像在我们中间》视频的一部分! 我们对新的飞船地图感到非常兴奋 谁还会认为现实生活中的《我们之间》会如此酷炫呢？🙋♀️

感谢波特兰精神号让我们在他们的船上拍摄！https://www.portlandspirit.com。

感谢来自She's Alaska的Cooper Grey帮助我们完成了这首歌曲。他的频道https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCcveoEbcHSG8M_uhWmJAhkg

如果你喜欢The Norris Nuts, Dixie D'Amelio, 或Txunamy, 你会喜欢我们的频道。我们做的是有趣的恶作剧、歌曲和短剧!

Shiloh的Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/shilohanelson/   
Elijah的Instagram：https://www.instagram.com/iamelijahnelson/
Micah的Instagram：https://www.instagram.com/heythisismicah/?hl=en
Judah的Instagram：https://www.instagram.com/judahnelson/?hl=en
布兰妮的Instagram：https://www.instagram.com/britneyleighnelson/
Aislinn的Instagram https://www.instagram.com/aislinnelimcc/?hl=en

歌曲作品。
作词人： 库珀-格雷（来自《她是阿拉斯加》） Cooper Grey (来自She's Alaska), Shiloh & Bros, Elijah Nelson, Shiloh Nelson, Britney Nelson.
音轨制作，混音和母带制作。Diego Fernandes
制作人： David Nelson 


在这里订阅！http://bit.ly/ShilohToJudahChannel

当我们发布新的视频时，点击铃铛以获得通知! 

#amongus #imposteramongus #inreallife

localize.description:
